Package sportstournament.gui

Class EndGameScreen

java.lang.Object
sportstournament.gui.Screen
sportstournament.gui.EndGameScreen
public class EndGameScreen extends Screen
This class implements the EndGameScreen which appears once all the weeks have been complete. It displays the team name, length of the season, money gained, and points gained.
Author:
Isaac Steele and Reuben Schoonbee
